Falcon's South African Shale Bid in Advanced Stage, Business Report Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-24T05:12:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/falcon-s-south-african-shale-bid-in-advanced-stage-business-report-says.html
Falcon Oil & Gas Ltd. (FO) ’s application
to explore for shale gas in South Africa’s Karoo is at an
advanced stage, Business Report said, citing Steve Mills, the
technical compliance manager of the Petroleum Agency of South
Africa.  Applications by  Royal Dutch Shell Plc (RDSA)  and  Sasol Ltd. (SOL)  may
take longer to process, the Johannesburg-based newspaper cited
Mills as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  